{"tid":2246365,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"穆迪下調英國債務評級至Aa3","createTime":"2020-10-17T03:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T03:59:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07d475b6106ee9be4f4bd54c72308f16b10357df","tid":2246365,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555221-20201017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555221-20201017.htm&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao%2F2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=4bc92e68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555221-20201017.htm&h=90929520\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555221-20201017.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n信貸評級機構穆迪投資下調英國主權債務評級，由「Aa2」調低至「Aa3」，展望評級就由「負面」調整至「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n穆迪在聲明中指出，英國決定脫歐，隨後亦無法達成貿易協議以維持接近歐盟成員國的利益，將加劇當地負面的財務結構。"}]}